  "prompt": "What is the best website to buy customized T-shirts in India?",
  "response": "There are several popular websites in India where you can buy customized T-shirts. Here are a few well-regarded options:\n\n1. **Printvenue**: Offers a wide range of customizable products, including T-shirts. You can upload your designs or use their design tools.\n\n2. **Vistaprint**: Known for its easy-to-use interface and variety of templates, Vistaprint allows you to create custom T-shirts for personal or business use.\n\n3. **Alma Mater**: This site specializes in creating customized T-shirts, hoodies, and other apparel. It is particularly popular for bulk orders.\n\n4. **Bewakoof**: Offers custom printing options alongside their own trendy designs. Known for quality apparel.\n\n5. **iLogo**: Ideal for bulk orders, iLogo allows customization with your own designs for T-shirts and other merchandise.\n\n6. **Inkmonk**: Offers a range of customizable products, including T-shirts, with an emphasis on high-quality printing and reliable delivery.\n\n7. **Redwolf**: Although better known for its own designs, Redwolf also offers custom printing options with a focus on quality.\n\nMake sure to compare prices, check reviews, and understand the delivery and return policies before making a purchase to ensure a satisfactory experience.",
